<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@3.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@3.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
      
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Education</h1>
        <p class="lead">Academic background and professional development</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h3>Computer Programming</h3>
          <p class="timeline-date">2024 - Present | Georgian College, Barrie, ON</p>
          <p>
            Advanced diploma program focusing on modern programming languages and software development.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Currently maintaining a high academic average while working full-time</li>
            <li>Learning JavaScript, Node.js, Python, C#, and database technologies</li>
            <li>Developing skills in web development, mobile app development, and software engineering</li>
            <li>Focusing on practical applications and industry-relevant projects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h3>Bachelor of Computer Science</h3>
          <p class="timeline-date">2014 - 2018 | Centro Universitário FIAP, São Paulo, Brazil</p>
          <p>
            Comprehensive undergraduate education in computer science fundamentals and software development.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Completed coursework in algorithms, data structures, and software engineering</li>
            <li>Participated in group projects developing web and mobile applications</li>
            <li>Studied database design, network infrastructure, and programming paradigms</li>
            <li>Gained foundation in theoretical and practical aspects of computer science</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Certifications & Professional Development</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h3 class="panel-title">Technical Certifications</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">ITIL Foundation</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Microsoft Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">CompTIA A+</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h3 class="panel-title">Additional Training</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">React Development Course</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Node.js Masterclass</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">ServiceNow Administration</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">JavaScript for Web Development</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@3.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
